    "The retriever searches for document sections that are semantically similar to the user's query, using cosine similarity to evaluate how closely related two vectors are within the embedding space.",
    "Equation ( 6) illustrates the concept of cosine similarity.",
    "cos(𝑢, 𝑣) =𝑢.𝑣 (‖𝑢‖|‖𝑣‖) (6) Cosine similarity scores range from -1 (completely dissimilar) to 1 (identical).",
    "The model retrieves the document sections with the highest cosine similarity scores, indicating their relevance to the user's query.",
    "These retrieved sections, along with the conversation context, are then fed into the Groq LLM."
